(E2- ES-EPC and E3- Full-EPC) Equal per capita convergence: Reflects a distribution of the budget to achieve equal-per-capita emissions in 2030. Thus, the calculation of country emission shares in 2030 is simply:5\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
